data.description: Beautiful two-story, three-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home.  Features this home includes are storage space, a large pantry, double sinks in the primary bathroom, recessed ceilings, high ceilings in the living area, and many more features.  Easy access to Gulf Freeway, Sam Houston Tollway, and minutes away from Hobby Airport.
